   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>CHAPTER NINE THE SPIRIT'S WORK ON AND IN</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>THE BELIEVERS 1 Scripture Reading: 1 Pet 1:2; Luke 15:8-9; John 16:8-11; Luke 15:18-24 OUTLINE Sanctifying the God-chosen people before they repent and believe 1 Pet 1:2:</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Seeking them carefully by enlightening them until finding them Luke 15:8-9.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Convicting them John 16:8-11: Concerning sin in Adam, not believing into Christ v. 9.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Concerning righteousness in Christ in His resurrection v. 10.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Concerning judgment with Satan unto eternal perdition v. 11.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Leading them to: Repent unto God Luke 15:18-21.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Receive Christ as their life supply Luke 15:22-24.</S>
